---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="SEC cybersecurity disclosure readiness for public companies. Meet disclosure requirements and demonstrate board-level cyber governance.">
  <HeroSection
    headline="SEC Cybersecurity Disclosure Readiness"
    subheadline="Meet SEC disclosure requirements. Demonstrate board-level cyber governance. Protect investor confidence."
    ctaText="Get Started"
    ctaHref="/about"
  />

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>Why SEC Cybersecurity Disclosure Matters</h2>
    <p>Public companies must disclose material cybersecurity incidents and describe their cyber risk governance. Without robust disclosure processes, companies face enforcement risk, investor concern, and reputational damage.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Meet SEC Disclosure Requirements</h3>
        <p>Public companies must disclose material cybersecurity incidents on Form 8-K within 4 business days of determining materiality &mdash; a tight timeline that demands established processes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Demonstrate Board Governance</h3>
        <p>Annual 10-K disclosures must describe board oversight of cybersecurity risk, including how the board is informed about and monitors cyber threats.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Protect Investor Confidence</h3>
        <p>Transparent cyber risk disclosure builds investor trust and reduces litigation risk. Investors expect companies to manage and disclose cyber risk proactively.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Establish Materiality Processes</h3>
        <p>Having a defined materiality determination process is critical for timely and accurate disclosure &mdash; without it, companies risk late filings or inadequate disclosures.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>How We Help</h2>
    <p>Four service packages designed to meet you where you are in your SEC cyber disclosure journey.</p>
    <div class="service-overview-grid">
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Readiness Sprint</h3>
        <p>Scope, assess, and plan in 2&#8211;4 weeks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Disclosure Program</h3>
        <p>Build materiality and filing processes</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Board Governance</h3>
        <p>Design board oversight and reporting</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Ongoing Compliance</h3>
        <p>Maintain disclosure readiness year-round</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're preparing for your first 10-K cyber disclosure or need help building incident-to-disclosure playbooks, we can help you meet SEC requirements with confidence.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Let's Talk</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card {
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-overview-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem var(--spacing-page);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
